Documentation is available at
http://www.varlena.com/Reports/Docs

Support and consulting is available
from ae Consulting at info@varlena.com.

The companion program ReRun is an example PostgreSQL/php/apache based 
utility which supports a report registry and running of reports from
a web page.  It is available under http://www.varlena.com/Reports.
